block.l: var crd = new List(), myself = this, options = { enableHighAccuracy: true, timeout: 5000, maximumAge: 0 }; function success(pos) { crd = new List([ pos.coords.latitude, pos.coords.longitude ]); } function error(err) { crd = new List([37.872099, -122.257852]); myself.inform('Warning:\nGeolocation failed.'); } navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition( success, error, options ); return function () {return crd; }
